code: @Override protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String clusterName, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     return new JGroupsEndpoint(uri, this, channel, clusterName, channelProperties, enableViewMessages). }
/**  * Channel to use  */ public void setChannel(JChannel channel) {     this.channel = channel. }

code: /**  * If set to true, the consumer endpoint will receive org.jgroups.View messages as well (not only org.jgroups.Message instances).  * By default only regular messages are consumed by the endpoint.  */ public void setEnableViewMessages(boolean enableViewMessages) {     this.enableViewMessages = enableViewMessages. }
